snippet.title: NCAA Football 14 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
NCAA Football 14 is available on July 9th. Download the NCAA 14 demo and per-order today! http://www.easports.com/ncaa-football

Experience the unpredictability and innovation unique to college football with the Infinity Engine. Get ready for unprecedented control and the most authentic, realistic NCAA Football 14 gameplay yet.
